gion\n|-\n!rowspan=\"29\" style=\"background-color: {{Welsh Labour/meta/color}}; width: 10px;\" |\n|rowspan=\"29\" | [[Welsh Labour|Labour]] (29)\n| [[Mick Antoniw]]\n| [[Pontypridd (Assembly constituency)|Pontypridd]]\n|-\n| [[Hannah Blythyn]]\n| [[Delyn (Assembly constituency)|Delyn]]\n|-\n| [[Dawn Bowden]]\n| [[Merthyr Tydfil and Rhymney (Assembly constituency)|Merthyr Tydfil and Rhymney]]\n|-\n| [[Jayne Bryant]]\n| [[Newport West (Assembly constituency)|Newport West]]\n|-\n| [[Hefin David]]\n| [[Caerphilly (Assembly constituency)|Caerphilly]]\n|-\n| [[Alun Davies (politician)|Alun Davies]]\n| [[Blaenau Gwent (Assembly constituency)|Blaenau Gwent]]\n|-\n| [[Mark Drakeford]]\n| [[Cardiff West (Assembly constituency)|Cardiff West]]\n|-\n| [[Rebecca Evans (politician)|Rebecca Evans]]\n| [[Gower (Assembly constituency)|Gower]]\n|-\n| [[Vaughan Gething]]\n| [[Cardiff South and Penarth (Assembly constituency)|Cardiff South and Penarth]]\n|-\n| [[John Griffiths (Welsh politician)|John Griffiths]]\n| [[Newport East (Assembly constituency)|Newport East]]\n|-\n| [[Lesley Griffiths]]\n| [[Wrexham (Assembly constituency)|Wrexham]]\n|-\n| [[Mike Hedges (politician)|Mike Hedges]]\n| [[Swansea East (Assembly constituency)|Swansea East]]\n|-\n| [[Vikki Howells]]\n| [[Cynon Valley (Assembly constituency)|Cynon Valley]]\n|-\n| [[Jane Hutt]]\n| [[Vale of Glamorgan (Assembly constituency)|Vale of Glamorgan]]\n|-\n| [[Huw Irranca-Davies]]\n| [[Ogmore (Assembly constituency)|Ogmore]]\n|-\n| [[Julie James]]\n| [[Swansea West (Assembly constituency)|Swansea West]]\n|-\n| [[Ann Jones (politician)|Ann Jones]]\n| [[Vale of Clwyd (Assembly constituency)|Vale of Clwyd]]\n|-\n| [[Carwyn Jones]]\n| [[Bridgend (Assembly constituency)|Bridgend]]\n|-\n| [[Jeremy Miles]]\n| [[Neath (Assembly constituency)|Neath]]\n|-\n| [[Eluned Morgan, Baroness Morgan of Ely|Baroness Eluned Morgan]]\n| [[Mid and West Wales (National Assembly for Wales electoral region)|Mid and West Wales]]\n|-\n| [[Julie Morgan]]